data.title: F65338 Force 10 3 burn marine electric cooker oven grill 230V Euro comp
data.meta_description: F65338 Force 10 3 burn marine electric cooker oven grill 240V Euro comp.  Ultimate marine cooker for sail and power boats.
data.text:
Force 10 3-Burner Electric -Oven & Grill-Gimbaled-240V Eurostd.

The ultimate cooker appliance for marine market in sail and power.

The 3 burner ceramic glass top range features 3 powerful 1200 watt top burners, and an oven and broiler. Features include a slide away door for maintaining gimbal, an oven light and a hot surface indicator light for safety.

This stylish stainless steel compact Range is designed to fit into smaller galley spaces. Features include a space saving foldaway door. Safety features include thermal overheat protection top burner element heat indicator, secondary door lock and comes complete with pot retention device. Models are available in either 120 or 230 Volt model and can operate at 50 or 60 Hz. The unit can be built in with the F70034 trim kit.

Force 10 has over 30 years of experience in the design and manufacture of gas and electric cooking appliances for the marine market. Force 10 is a subsidiary of the French company Groupe ENO. Combined, Force 10 and ENO are the world market leader in marine cooking appliances. Force 10 products are represented in over 15 different countries and we can supply spare parts worldwide.

Force 10 Galley Ranges are sought after by sailors who demand the best. Our reputation for quality and customer service has been one of the contributing factors to our success.

Space saving slide away oven door.
